{"tid":1261069,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【進擊白區】會唔會有人成立「佛系政黨」？","createTime":"2019-06-27T05:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T06:52:00.000Z","uid":263448,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d070cfd06dc9de5c484503e724c67ee6657d698","tid":1261069,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有鑑於今屆政府，好多人覺醒咗，發現好多自動當選既白區。<br />\n我地雖然叫咗好多人做選民，但每4個就有1個有票無得投。<br />\n<br />\n有啲人已經搞緊新政黨，但動員力，資源，都未必夠多夠好。而且好多都1516，唔知打唔打得贏，就會猶豫，甚至撞車！！<br />\n<br />\n而更重要係，<span style=\"color: red;\">參選人不足</span>！！<br />\n太多人怕出面，又覺得自己背景學歷人脈不足，而卻步。<br />\n當你泛民都派新仔出去，可能多咗幾個地方有選，都依然係有白區存在！<br />\n依然有好多居民因為無人參選，無得換馬！！<br />\n<br />\n我認為，參選門檻低，只要3000蚊10個當地推薦人，就可以入場，咁倒不如成立一個「佛系黨」，用最少成本達到最大效果！！<br />\n<br />\n攻略：<br />\n1.黨名叫「佛系」專門參選啲確定白區/未知白區/危險白區。<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">叫得「佛系」就只需要付出入場費3000蚊，之後乜都唔做，如果咁都勝選，咁果區保皇黨真係好仆街，仆街到無倫果種。</span><br />\n3.如果最後有其他新政黨撞區，但確定係自己人，選民自然唔會去投「佛系」，好難話撞到車。<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: red;\">保皇黨因為知道有其他參選人，所以點都會加大開支，造成混亂。</span><br />\n5.「佛系」唔需要太大背景，只要有人願意企出黎，搵齊10個當地人推薦就可以出戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1.需要籌款，3000蚊玩一玩，未必有人願意出戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">需要為「佛系」呢個策略眾籌</span>，要成立一個「佛系聯盟」再分配資源。<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">有幸當選，就要負責社區責任</span>，需要搵一班有才能既人幫你，同埋做實事，咁先對得住選民，之後就要轉黨出去或者獨立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「佛系」<br />\n政見：當選與否，一切隨緣。如有幸當選，定必盡心為社區。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無用，我唔識太多野，如果有人認同支持，歡迎接手計劃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016fad6c957e1cf357fb83317480f5b4aabe570a","tid":1261069,"uid":156511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"點解仲未有人搞香港共產黨"},{"pid":"c6796ecb042b846d72cc189cac387ce393eadf7b","tid":1261069,"uid":80125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74dbfa9c8bb9a56368eab04f7c679e6963ab1ddd","tid":1261069,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79129d3772a9d032f4eb9f6f197fbb0d6c9cd2f","tid":1261069,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n幾好笑 但3000蚊搞一搞建制派都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8d62ad792c354989f242ab525c3e7d538bddc6","tid":1261069,"uid":16775,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"如果選既搵個有心既真係落區關心下公公婆婆<br />\nAnyway 我係贊成呢個玩法 好過得白票投"},{"pid":"11a0fb36d3466fb188dc34b210868715e4a95f12","tid":1261069,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"我唔識搞眾籌，資源分配，地區分配，法律文件等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果計劃覺得好既，希望有搞手搞。<br />\n成立咗之後，雖然有部份錢係丟落海咁。<br />\n但總好過有咁多白區。<br />\n參選成本低咗，啲有顧忌既人都可以放手一搏，好似買六合彩咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1d465bb985eaac8a4ce9658411891cd6c6865c","tid":1261069,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"現在大多數參與區選的 候選人，也沒有想過怎樣為香港贏取這場抗爭，他們出來不滿建制派壟斷 ，也曾經試圖做一些事情，限止建制派大穫全勝！"},{"pid":"2c5cc6325012d6e0b597cb7687c2968f68214751","tid":1261069,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"眾籌3千蚊輕鬆啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我支持"},{"pid":"39b3c4a53bce0b16430b8033e19eac83a5872c72","tid":1261069,"uid":263448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c5cc6325012d6e0b597cb7687c2968f68214751","tid":1261069,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"眾籌3千蚊輕鬆啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"我意思係，成立一個佛系聯盟，負責眾籌經費，管理派遺。<br />\n唔係只籌3千蚊....<br />\n<br />\n假設最後香港有50個白區，未有任何政黨表明參選，咁就要搵50個人去佛，一共要15萬。<br />\n參加佛系計劃既候選人無須高學歷，但要有心。<br />\n例如你只係普通既IT狗，眼見咁多白區唔想保皇黨自動當選，但又怕自己係隻普通IT狗唔夠爭，就可以參加呢計劃，承諾自己如果幸運勝選就要熱心社區。你出樣，我地出錢，其他乜都唔洗做(但必要既露面/辯論就一定出席)"},{"pid":"9782cd6e3f244b5a2dc32c1c621bdf7d394fba17","tid":1261069,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65930e703c55ee8e5f832027e863b3814d6e6648","tid":1261069,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kUFa5HJ.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUFa5HJ.png&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dopBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=251e8094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kUFa5HJ.png</a>"},{"pid":"9b16911af9b504ba1bef0ad6d6d35554c89c23e0","tid":1261069,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kUFa5HJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUFa5HJ.png&h=46be4a97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca9d2b16f5a18c6252b5f098c51d38b029c90014","tid":1261069,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"無限支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞得成我第一個捐錢"},{"pid":"22dbb882f32e1149eca02339a568d0e5044189fb","